{"tid":545930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google攜手HTC 臺北成亞太最大研發地","createTime":"2018-01-31T04:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T08:03:18.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b6582c62d43e53b99fe60e5bdf4da802327ab564","tid":545930,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:22:20.000Z","msg":"【看中國2018年1月31日訊】（看中國記者明思綜合報導）臺灣宏達電(HTC)去年（2017年）九月將手機代工部門出售給Google後，總交易金額達11億美元(約新台幣330億元)。Google硬體資深副總裁奧斯特羅（Rick Osterloh）1月30日表示，歡迎HTC團隊加入Google，臺北也正式成為Google在亞太區最大的研發基地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2018/1-31/p2089141a923505116-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2018%2F1-31%2Fp2089141a923505116-ss.jpg&h=64c6504b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《雅虎》報導稱，Google與宏達電(HTC)正式完成11億美元合作協議，Google硬體資深副總裁歐斯特羅（Rick Osterloh）29日發文宣布，HTC團隊的優秀成員加入Google後，他們將會為Google注入數十年專注於智慧型手機領域的經驗，成為未來Google創新產品的一大助力。<br />\n<br />\n歐斯特羅指出，在Google發展硬體事業進入第三年之際，將繼續致力於長期建置與投資，未來Google和新成員將全心投入，透過Google人工智慧（AI）技術與軟硬整合，創造出改善用戶生活的體驗。<br />\n<br />\n歐斯特羅還特別稱讚了去年發布的第二代Made by Google產品，他表示，從用戶反饋中得知，Google研發的新產品為人們的生活帶來了許多便利，例如用Pixel 2拍出漂亮的照片、用Google Home Mini享受免手持的自在輕鬆，或用Google Pixel Buds無線耳機感受支援40種語言的即時翻譯等。<br />\n<br />\n不過，奧斯特羅也坦言，「Google的硬體之路才剛剛起步，打造硬體這件事可是很硬的，我們前方的路還很長。」<br />\n<br />\n而對於新協議的完成，宏達電（HTC）董事長王雪紅則表示，「今天HTC已開啟了嶄新的一頁，我們將以自有品牌智慧型手機與虛擬實境系統HTC VIVE，繼續引領創新。我們相信HTC優秀的研發團隊、聚焦重點營運的策略以及挹注的資源，能使HTC專注研發新一代的行動裝置產品，為全球消費者帶來創新的行動生活體驗，並為股東們創造長期利益。」<br />\n<br />\n據《聯合報》消息稱，自Google與宏達電HTC在2017年9月對外宣布合作協議後，根據該協議的內容，Google延攬原參與打造Google Pixel系列手機的HTC成員加入Google，HTC也將其智慧財產權非專屬授權予Google使用。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，在人工智慧已逐漸邁向人們生活的今天，不僅Google看上臺灣優異的硬體開發技術，連微軟也看上臺灣優秀的硬體工程人才，因此日前也投資10億美元，在臺灣成立AI研發中心。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，在Google與宏達電（HTC）今次交易完成後，HTC將「更聚焦於自有品牌智慧型手機業務」，HTC也將「構建虛擬實境生態系統，擴展VIVE版圖，繼續投入物聯網、擴增實境和人工智慧等領域的創新」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2018/01/31/848727.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F848727.html&d=LRUMzfhORgM2aOm%2BMWXlhdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=cdd39ba1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2018/01/31/848727.html</a>"},{"pid":"b6b343fa42827bad550a6d4d7352d239effd7067","tid":545930,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:24:06.000Z","msg":"Apple Google Amazon MS全部都去哂台灣搞研發"},{"pid":"8e217914f9c32f2ec7fcd71a22346bb8aadd7122","tid":545930,"uid":50301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"吔htc仲未收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a38faa0b7fa7c52072a8677788ee333624643dd","tid":545930,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:25:53.000Z","msg":"去深圳同騰訊華為合作好過啦"},{"pid":"79a7442cc0ddf65f96436722d8331c5883b9c60d","tid":545930,"uid":11001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b6b343fa42827bad550a6d4d7352d239effd7067","tid":545930,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:24:06.000Z","msg":"Apple Google Amazon MS全部都去哂台灣搞研發"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:27:18.000Z","msg":"唔通去支那搏俾人抄咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f0700aa9334f2e3a7b602c6a7530898a12260f","tid":545930,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:27:21.000Z","msg":"新北市+1"},{"pid":"ab4f4e973986a6a4f097e712985705459585d4a5","tid":545930,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b6b343fa42827bad550a6d4d7352d239effd7067","tid":545930,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:24:06.000Z","msg":"Apple Google Amazon MS全部都去哂台灣搞研發"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:27:24.000Z","msg":"心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看好台灣人才及市場地位，微軟投資 10 億成立 AI 研發中心<br />\n<a href=\"http://technews.tw/2018/01/10/mircrosoft-ai-taiwan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2Fmircrosoft-ai-taiwan%2F&d=LRUMzfhORgM2aOm%2BMWXlhdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9cca9578\" target=\"_blank\">http://technews.tw/2018/01/10/mircrosoft-ai-taiwan/</a>"},{"pid":"5b5255598a374fbc7042abd4074be46be961c564","tid":545930,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e217914f9c32f2ec7fcd71a22346bb8aadd7122","tid":545930,"uid":50301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"吔htc仲未收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:29:05.000Z","msg":"HTC = Help This Company~ 無咁快收皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be858f1273c7268feaa85ef3236b6182e85906b","tid":545930,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"打造硬體這件事可是很硬的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84855d1dead11a7850d8e4d1f19739117982edc","tid":545930,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ab4f4e973986a6a4f097e712985705459585d4a5","tid":545930,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b6b343fa42827bad550a6d4d7352d239effd7067","tid":545930,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:24:06.000Z","msg":"Apple Google Amazon MS全部都去哂台灣搞研發"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:27:24.000Z","msg":"心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看好台灣人才及市場地位，微軟投資 10 億成立 AI 研發中心<br />\n<a href=\"http://technews.tw/2018/01/10/mircrosoft-ai-taiwan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3